{
  "stem": "1061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no say on what we would be doing, whether we would be planning to run away or not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was very young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My two sisters were truly in charge of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In every respect, they-- they were father and mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even though Father was in the same camp, he was with the men so that we saw him every now and then.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But basically, I was being mothered by my two sisters, and it was not for me to decide whether or not we will go as the others did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as soon as the shooting started that night, where the heaps of bodies were found at the opening of that fence.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One woman running either toward-- toward the-- the fence or away from the fence-- I can't tell-- was caught in the middle, and she was shot.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She died in the worst agony of yelling and crying all night long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You see, the others that were shot at the-- at the fence were all dead, because obviously, the guards were right over them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I imagine that this was-- the fact that she was left to-- in the agony of this for hours, screaming and yelling, was probably done on purpose, because she could have just as well have been shot like the others were.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will never forget the agony.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she kept yelling that her legs were shot off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever it was, I-- I cannot begin to tell you [SIGHS] what it-- what it felt like because at this point, we knew that something horrible was going to be happening to us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we just didn't know how we were going to perish, you see?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whether we were going to perish like this woman, left to die in agony for hours rather than be finished off, or whether we gonna be in a heap like these people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sure enough, next day, we were loaded on trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were you aware of this plan to escape beforehand?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, as I'm telling-- as I told you, I was always protected.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even though my parents-- my father was a-- in the camp, but he didn't mix.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even though this was not a family unit, my sisters were still my protectors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was told what to do, and I did it because I loved them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and we're very close to this day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I loved them dearly, and they loved me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, now we do this, and now we do that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it never really-- my input was zero, because all I had to do is to be alert of what was happening around.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But decisions for escape or such, that-- really, I mean, I was really too young to-- and I was, don't forget, I was by then very skinny.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was a skinny child to begin with, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then with the malnutrition and the starvation and all these.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You had boils.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Every now and then, I had boils.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's-- you know, this is all a result of malnutrition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all these things that-- that combined to make you a wreck of a human being were visible in all of us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But because we were so tightly knit-- and we also had, they had, friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had friends, you know, who participated in this kind of support-- you see?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The school friends, the friends of the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I shouldn't be saying that, but-- because human beings know how to-- how to come across when there's need, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When people see a little kid, and it's full of lice and starved to death, and she's all left alone, somebody will hug her, you see?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the world is like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On one end, you have this horror of the German beast with the dogs or the Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the other hand, you have this little old lady who will hug a little skinny kid filled with, covered with lice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So anyhow, my sisters were my protectors, and they were my guardians, and they were-- they were my surrogate parents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, the fact that every now and then we could see Father-- you know, wave to him or whatever-- was very helpful.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We lived in barracks, of course, in that camp, [INAUDIBLE] But in the last camp where the breakout took place, that-- I don't even remember if there was a real camp or if they would just dumped us there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was transitional in a way of it probably took a day or two or three at the most.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
